    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/holcombe-moor-firing-times"/>
    <title>Holcombe Moor Firing Times</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Holcombe Moor’s Firing Times are presented in three file formats so that the information is accessible to everyone. The TXT format is browseable on mobile devices such as Blackberry’s, smart phones and tablets. The CSV format enables the MOD to post information on data.gov.uk, and therefore remain transparent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
