    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/lulworth-firing-notice"/>
    <title>Lulworth Firing Notice</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Lulworth Firing Times are presented in three file formats so that the information is accessible to everyone. The TXT format is readable on mobile devices such as Blackberry’s, smart phones and tablets. The CSV format enables the MOD to post information on data.gov.uk, and therefore remain transparent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
