    <title>Senior Officers of the Armed Forces: hospitality received</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;In addition to publishing the hospitality received of our most senior Civil Servants, the Ministry of Defence will now be publishing the hospitality received of the most senior Officers of the Armed Forces on a quarterly basis.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
