    <title>Senior Officers of the Armed Forces: business expenses</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;In addition to publishing the business expenses incurred by the most senior Civil Servants on official duty, the Ministry of Defence will now be publishing the business expenses of the most senior Officers of the Armed Forces on a quarterly basis.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
