    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since 24 January 2012, the Department for Communities and Local Government has published salary details for consenting senior staff earning more than £58,200. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is in line with the &lt;a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/local-authority-data-transparency-code"&gt;Local authority data transparency code&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
